export const translationsEn = {
  IntroHeader: "Invest For The Future",
  IntroText: "If you're looking for an investment firm to provide disciplined investing strategies, offer straightforward market perspective and help you navigate market volatility, then you have come to the right place.",
  IntroBtn: "Learn More",
  PerksHeader: "Perks You Enjoy.",
  PerksSub: "We have built a robust system to help you manage and increase your income greatly",
  Security: "Security",
  SecurityText: "All investments are held in safe custody by a licensed securities custodian which protects all investments. We are protected by the Securities & Exchange Commission.",
  EasyAccess: "Easy Access",
  EasyText: "We aren’t rigid with our investment options. It doesn’t matter who you bank with, you can access our product offerings.",
  Withdrawal: "Easy Withdrawal",
  WithdrawalText: "Supply your crypto details, enter an amount you wish to withdraw, and confirm your transaction to withdraw your money.",
  Support: "Excellent Support",
  SupportText: "Our support team is always ready to respond to whatever concerns you may have.",
};
export const translationsCH = {
  IntroHeader: "为未来投资",
  IntroText: "如果您正在寻找一家投资公司来提供严格的投资策略、提供直接的市场观点并帮助您应对市场波动，那么您来对地方了。",
  IntroBtn: "学到更多",
  PerksHeader: "您享受的特权。",
  PerksSub: "我们建立了一个强大的系统来帮助您管理和大大增加您的收入",
  Security: "安全",
  SecurityText: "所有投资均由持牌证券托管人安全保管，以保护所有投资。 我们受到证券交易委员会的保护。",
  EasyAccess: "容易接近",
  EasyText: "我们对投资选择并不严格。 无论您与谁合作，您都可以访问我们的产品。",
  Withdrawal: "轻松提款",
  WithdrawalText: "提供您的加密详细信息，输入您希望提取的金额，并确认您的交易以提取您的资金。",
  Support: "优秀的支持",
  SupportText: "我们的支持团队随时准备响应您可能遇到的任何问题。",
};
